<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> حسن صحيح - <span class="c2">((المشكاة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٨٤٣ و ٢٨٤٤)</span> , <span class="c2">((البيوع)</span>): ق مختصراً.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>